#. type: Content of: <pre>
#: src/lessons/lander/universe/DelegatingLanderWorld.html:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[!java|c]double [/!]getAngle()[!scala]:Double[/!]\n"
"[!java|c]void [/!]setDesiredAngle([!java|c]double "
"[/!]desiredAngle[!scala]:Double[/!])"
